The Nelson Mandela Bay Municipality says there will be a closure of a section of Walker Drive Road on Friday at the intersection of Kabega Road to excavate, remove the existing pipe and relay it with a new 500mm pipe."The water supply will not be affected in any way," the municipality said."The date and time of road closure is Friday 9th June 19:00 / 7pm - Monday 12th June 06:00 / 6am"Traffic will be diverted as per the image."Kabega Road will not be closed or affected.